Map from M.I.A. Jailbreak, dated 10/11/2008.

This is a beta version of Wakka and is unfortunately the only copy I have of this map from M.I.A. As such, some areas on the map are unfinished. Wakka was created by the M.I.A.P.D. (Senior Admin) Wakka for M.I.A. 24/7 Jailbreak, and is mostly a compilation of several maps, these being:

- ba_jail_nitrox
- ba_jail_lakeprison
- ba_jail_cec
- ba_jail_mars
- ba_jail_maximum
